Screenshots, logs, and documents help engineers resolve issues faster.

## Why Attach Files?

**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ Engineers see exact error
- ‚úÖ Faster diagnosis
- ‚úÖ Fewer clarification questions
- ‚úÖ Better solutions
- ‚úÖ Reduced resolution time

**"A picture is worth 1000 words"** - especially for tech support!

## Supported File Types

### ‚úÖ Accepted Formats

**Documents:**
- PDF (.pdf)
- Microsoft Word (.doc, .docx)
- Microsoft Excel (.xls, .xlsx)
- Text files (.txt, .log, .csv)

**Images:**
- JPEG (.jpg, .jpeg)
- PNG (.png)
- GIF (.gif)
- BMP (.bmp)
- WebP (.webp)

**Archives:**
- ZIP (.zip)
- RAR (.rar)
- 7-Zip (.7z)

### ‚ùå Blocked Formats (Security)

**Executables:**
- .exe, .bat, .cmd, .sh
- .dll, .sys, .msi
- .app, .dmg

**Scripts:**
- .js, .vbs, .ps1
- .py, .rb (unless in ZIP)

**Workaround:** ZIP blocked files first, then upload ZIP.

## Size Limits

**Per File:**
- Maximum: **10 MB**
- Minimum: No limit

**Per Ticket:**
- Maximum files: **5 files**
- Maximum total: **50 MB**

**If File Too Large:**
1. Compress as ZIP
2. Use cloud storage (Google Drive, Dropbox)
3. Share link in ticket comments
4. Split into smaller files

